      "content": "the patches and stretching aren't doing anything for this level of pain. i'm just worried that if i wait 8 hours between pills, the pain will spike so high i won't be able to function. people online say that as long as the total mg is okay you can space them out however you want. if i take 400mg every 2 hours, that's only 4800mg in 24 hours, which isn't even that crazy right? just tell me if that's a safe way to handle this so i can get back to work.",
